properties.areaDesc: Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI; Green Bay south of line from  Oconto WI to Little Sturgeon Bay WI; Sturgeon Bay to Two Rivers WI
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 4 at 3:18PM CST until January 6 at 2:00AM CST by NWS Green Bay WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest to west winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35
kt expected.

* WHERE...Green Bay south of line from Oconto WI to Little
Sturgeon Bay WI, Sturgeon Bay to Two Rivers WI and Lake
Michigan from Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI.

* WHEN...From 10 AM Sunday to 2 AM CST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM SUNDAY TO 2 AM CST MONDAY
